content: Hi everyone :wave: I'm Max, I did a couple of tiny doc fixes in 2014 and wrote a bunch of rust code in 2015 but haven't really touched anything since then (most of my work has been happening in the Ruby and C# world(s?)). That said I've been following the project with a lot of excitement for a while and randomly seeing the tweet about helping with the compiler got me here :)

@Maximilian Haack I'd suggest you to read https://rust-lang.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/212497-t-compiler.2Fhelp-wanted/topic/Aman and https://rust-lang.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/212497-t-compiler.2Fhelp-wanted/topic/welcome
I think most of the info is around there
